casebody.data:
TUCSON LOT 4 LLC
v.
SUNQUEST INFORMATION et al. CV-16-0316-PR (23) Supreme Court of Arizona. May 15, 2017

MINUTES

ORDERED: Petition for Review = DENIED.

FURTHER ORDERED: Request for Attorneys' Fees (Appellees Sunquest Information Systems Inc.) = DENIED.

FURTHER ORDERED: Request for Attorneys' Fees (Appellant Tucson 4 LLC) = DENIED.

FURTHER ORDERED: The Court of Appeals' Opinion shall not be published, pursuant to Rule 111(g), Arizona Rules of the Supreme Court.

Justice Gould voted to grant review.
